summary:
Please provide evidence of your baseline configuration hardening process (GCP configurations). This may include:

Server deployment checklists outlining manual hardening steps;
Automated scripts (e.g. Terraform, Ansible, etc.) to deploy servers with baseline configurations automatically;
Infrastructure as code scripts to provision servers with baseline configurations;
Internal technical guides with specific hardening steps.

Can you provide screenshots of any internal guides in Wikis (e.g. Notion, Confluence, Github, Google Drive, etc.) that address:

Hardening guides;
Configuration, installation, and operation of the information system;
Screenshot showing who has access to the above-mentioned guide(s). 
Internal Support Channels & Example of 1 report internal incident

Please provide:
1. Screenshot(s) of where these policies and procedures are stored;
2. Who at the company can view them;
3. The most recent approval for each policy (if not captured in the policy itself).

Please provide system screenshots showing the following as it pertains to system backups:

1. Backup Frequency (Please skip, already uploaded in Hyperproof);
2. Retention Settings;
3. Recent Backup Log (Please skip, already uploaded in Hyperproof);
4. Alert/Notification settings in the event of failed backup;
5. Example Alert.
